title.narrative: Capacity of key government institutions at district and community levels to provide and monitor quality health, HIV, nutrition and sanitation services, in regular and emergency situations, is strengthened

description.narrative: This Output was the major contributor to Outcome's achievement and the success obtained in its implementation was a direct implication on quality health of the targeted groups. The results achieved, which have contributing for the maternal, newborn and young child mortality reduction, as well as the stunting reduction has been strictly aligned with regional priorities. KRC1's reach was at the top of interventions. UNICEF's effective response to a malaria epidemic emergency, which contributed to its quick control, without any case of mortality, also constituted a strong UNICEF contribution as one of the main Government's partners in pursuing the SDG. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/02/2020
